n</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Refresh token</td><td style=\"text-align:left\">Used to refresh and obtain new authorization token after the authorization token expires, the refresh token also has a validity period.</td></tr></tbody></table></div><a name=\"Related-products\"></a><h3 id=\"38070661\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h3 \"><span data-id=\"38070661\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M574 665.4a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L446.5 781.6c-53.8 53.8-144.6 59.5-204 0-59.5-59.5-53.8-150.2 0-204l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.8-39.8a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L191.4 526.5c-84.6 84.6-84.6 221.5 0 306s221.5 84.6 306 0l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3L574 665.4zm258.6-474c-84.6-84.6-221.5-84.6-306 0L410.3 307.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.7 39.7c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c53.8-53.8 144.6-59.5 204 0 59.5 59.5 53.8 150.2 0 204L665.3 562.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.8 39.8c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c84.5-84.6 84.5-221.5 0-306.1zM610.1 372.3a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L372.3 598.7a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.6 39.6c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l226.4-226.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.5-39.6z\"></path></svg></span></span>Related products</h3><p><a href=\"https://miniprogram.gcash.com/docs/miniprogram_gcash/mpdev-old/api_openapi_obtainbasicmemberinformation\" data-idocs-page-id=\"52b466f1-3824-4aeb-ab07-d6eaf3dfe3d8\" data-idocs-page-slug=\"api_openapi_obtainbasicmemberinformation\"><strong>Obtain Basic Member Information</strong></a></p><a name=\"Scopes-List\"></a><h2 id=\"2d0f2057\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h2 \"><span data-id=\"2d0f2057\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\