module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M574 665.4a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L446.5 781.6c-53.8 53.8-144.6 59.5-204 0-59.5-59.5-53.8-150.2 0-204l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.8-39.8a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L191.4 526.5c-84.6 84.6-84.6 221.5 0 306s221.5 84.6 306 0l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3L574 665.4zm258.6-474c-84.6-84.6-221.5-84.6-306 0L410.3 307.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.7 39.7c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c53.8-53.8 144.6-59.5 204 0 59.5 59.5 53.8 150.2 0 204L665.3 562.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.8 39.8c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c84.5-84.6 84.5-221.5 0-306.1zM610.1 372.3a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L372.3 598.7a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.6 39.6c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l226.4-226.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.5-39.6z\"></path></svg></span></span>Access Process</h3><p>Obtain user information as an example, the overall access process is as follows (if you need to authorize other information, you only need to use a different scope for the scopes parameter when calling getAuthCode).<br><img alt=\"User authorization\" src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_150082/afts/img/A*bm4uRLKiV9wAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ#alt=image.png\" style=\"max-width:600px\" class=\"docs-image loaded showImg\" data-src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_150082/afts/img/A*bm4uRLKiV9wAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ#alt=image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p><a name=\"App-Obtains-Authcode\"></a><h3 id=\"64021544\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h3 \"><span data-id=\"64021544\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M574 665.4a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L446.5 781.6c-53.8 53.8-144.6 59.5-204 0-59.5-59.5-53.8-150.2 0-204l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.8-39.8a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L191.4 526.5c-84.6 84.6-84.6 221.5 0 306s221.5 84.6 306 0l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3L574 665.4zm258.6-474c-84.6-84.6-221.5-84.6-306 0L410.3 307.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.7 39.7c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c53.8-53.8 144.6-59.5 204 0 59.5 59.5 53.8 150.2 0 204L665.3 562.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.8 39.8c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c84.5-84.6 84.5-221.5 0-306.1zM610.1 372.3a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L372.3 598.7a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.6 39.6c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l226.4-226.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.5-39.6z\"></path></svg></span></span>App Obtains Authcode</h3><p>The user authorization is obtained by calling the jsapi <a href=\"https://miniprogram.gcash.com/docs/miniprogram_gcash/mpdev-old/api_openapi_getauthcode\" data-idocs-page-id=\"40ab6ee6-f245-46b1-85d7-3ec96230fdce\" data-idocs-page-slug=\"api_openapi_getauthcode\">my.getAuthCode</a>, and the authcode can be obtained in the success callback. The js code is as follows:</p><div class=\"styles-module_copyWrapper__Fc5qV\"><div class=\"styles-module_copyButton__vn-Pc\"><svg class=\"icon icon-copy\" viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"#ccc\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M832 64H296c-4.4 0-8 3.6-8 8v56c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8h496v688c0 4.4 3.6 8 8 8h56c4.4 0 8-3.6 8-8V96c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32zM704 192H192c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32v530.7c0 8.5 3.4 16.6 9.4 22.6l173.3 173.3c2.2 2.2 4.7 4 7.4 5.5v1.9h4.2c3.5 1.3 7.2 2 11 2H704c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32V224c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32zM350 856.2L263.9 770H350v86.2zM664 888H414V746c0-22.1-17.9-40-40-40H232V264h432v624z\"></path></svg>copy</div><pre style=\"display:block;overflow-x:auto;padding:0.5em;color:#383a42;background:#fafafa;transition:background var(--transition-delay)\"><code class=\"language-javascript\" style=\"white-space:pre\"><span>my.getAuthCode({\n</span><span>  </span><span style=\"color:#986801\">scopes</span><span>: [</span><span style=\"color:#50a14f\">'USER_ID'</span><span>],\n</span><span>  </span><span style=\"color:#986801\">success</span><span>: </span><span class=\"hljs-function\">(</span><span class=\"hljs-function hljs-params\">res</span><span class=\"hljs-function\">) =&gt;</span><span> {\n</span>    my.alert({\n<span>      </span><span style=\"color:#986801\">content</span><span>: res.authCode,\n</span>    });\n<!-- -->  },\n<span>  </span><span style=\"color:#986801\">failed</span><span>: </span><span class=\"hljs-function\">(</span><span class=\"hljs-function hljs-params\">res</span><span class=\"hljs-function\">) =&gt;</span><span> {\n</span><span>      </span><span style=\"color:#c18401\">console</span><span>.log(res.authErrorScopes)\n</span>  },\n<!-- -->});</code></pre></div><a name=\"Server-Obtains-Access-Token\"></a><h3 id=\"1387e7df\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h3 \"><span data-id=\"1387e7df\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M574 665.4a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L446.5 781.6c-53.8 53.8-144.6 59.5-204 0-59.5-59.5-53.8-150.2 0-204l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.8-39.8a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L191.4 526.5c-84.6 84.6-84.6 221.5 0 306s221.5 84.6 306 0l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3L574 665.4zm258.6-474c-84.6-84.6-221.5-84.6-306 0L410.3 307.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.7 39.7c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c53.8-53.8 144.6-59.5 204 0 59.5 59.5 53.8 150.2 0 204L665.3 562.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.8 39.8c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c84.5-84.6 84.5-221.5 0-306.1zM610.1 372.3a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L372.3 598.7a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.6 39.6c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l226.4-226.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.5-39.6z\"></path></svg></span></span>Server Obtains Access Token</h3><p>Merchant server can call <code>v1/authorizations/applyToken</code> interface in exchange for the access_token，developers can exchange access_token and userId with the obtained auth_code。auth_code as a ticket in exchange for access_token。<br></p><a name=\"Call-The-Server-Business-API\"></a><h3 id=\"9763e560\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h3 \"><span data-id=\"9763e560\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M574 665.4a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L446.5 781.6c-53.8 53.8-144.6 59.5-204 0-59.5-59.5-53.8-150.2 0-204l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.8-39.8a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L191.4 526.5c-84.6 84.6-84.6 221.5 0 306s221.5 84.6 306 0l116.2-116.2c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3L574 665.4zm258.6-474c-84.6-84.6-221.5-84.6-306 0L410.3 307.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.7 39.7c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c53.8-53.8 144.6-59.5 204 0 59.5 59.5 53.8 150.2 0 204L665.3 562.6a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.8 39.8c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l116.2-116.2c84.5-84.6 84.5-221.5 0-306.1zM610.1 372.3a8.03 8.03 0 00-11.3 0L372.3 598.7a8.03 8.03 0 000 11.3l39.6 39.6c3.1 3.1 8.2 3.1 11.3 0l226.4-226.4c3.1-3.1 3.1-8.2 0-11.3l-39.5-39.6z\"></path></svg></span></span>Call The Server Business API</h3><p>After obtaining access_token, developers can continue to use the token to call other authorization interface. Please pay attention to the permission scope and timeliness of the token.<br></p><a name=\"API-List\"></a><h2 id=\"c0bf73d2\" class=\"styles-module_anchored__AxVRP h2 \"><span data-id=\"c0bf73d2\" class=\"index-module_anchor__UrjO7 styles-module_anchorLink__mbBm1\"><span role=\"img\" aria-label=\"link\" class=\"anticon anticon-link\"><svg viewBox=\"64 64 896 896\" focusable=\"false\" data-icon=\"link\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-